WEBVTT

00:00:23.516 --> 00:00:30.796 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:00:31.296 --> 00:00:31.926 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Hi, everybody.

00:00:32.266 --> 00:00:33.596 A:middle
My name is Pedraum Pardehpoosh.

00:00:33.596 --> 00:00:34.966 A:middle
I run Product for the App Store.

00:00:34.966 --> 00:00:36.046 A:middle
Thanks for joining us today.

00:00:36.876 --> 00:00:38.296 A:middle
We've brought a few people

00:00:38.296 --> 00:00:40.176 A:middle
together that normally don't get

00:00:40.176 --> 00:00:41.066 A:middle
out of the office.

00:00:41.116 --> 00:00:42.286 A:middle
So this is going to be a session

00:00:42.286 --> 00:00:43.236 A:middle
that might be a little different

00:00:43.236 --> 00:00:44.276 A:middle
than what you're used to here.

00:00:44.276 --> 00:00:46.336 A:middle
It's a deeper look into the App

00:00:46.336 --> 00:00:46.936 A:middle
Store.

00:00:47.316 --> 00:00:48.296 A:middle
And I'm thrilled that you joined

00:00:48.296 --> 00:00:48.576 A:middle
us.

00:00:49.566 --> 00:00:50.486 A:middle
You heard about the App Store

00:00:50.486 --> 00:00:51.446 A:middle
from Phil on Monday at the

00:00:51.446 --> 00:00:51.976 A:middle
keynote.

00:00:52.526 --> 00:00:53.846 A:middle
And the staggering numbers that

00:00:53.846 --> 00:00:55.846 A:middle
demonstrate what a smash hit

00:00:55.846 --> 00:00:56.286 A:middle
it's been.

00:00:57.096 --> 00:00:59.036 A:middle
But today we're going to spend a

00:00:59.036 --> 00:01:00.146 A:middle
little time giving you an

00:01:00.146 --> 00:01:01.306 A:middle
overview of the App Store.

00:01:01.306 --> 00:01:02.086 A:middle
Go a little deeper.

00:01:03.446 --> 00:01:04.356 A:middle
We'll look at the design

00:01:04.356 --> 00:01:05.616 A:middle
philosophy that went into the

00:01:05.616 --> 00:01:06.956 A:middle
"why" we did it.

00:01:08.146 --> 00:01:10.246 A:middle
And we'll go a little deeper

00:01:10.246 --> 00:01:11.866 A:middle
into our emphasis on editorial.

00:01:12.756 --> 00:01:14.026 A:middle
Finally, we'll bring it all back

00:01:14.026 --> 00:01:15.206 A:middle
and talk about the implications

00:01:15.206 --> 00:01:17.116 A:middle
to you, the developers that

00:01:17.116 --> 00:01:17.716 A:middle
bring it to life.

00:01:19.076 --> 00:01:19.686 A:middle
Let's get started.

00:01:19.686 --> 00:01:21.806 A:middle
Who remembers this?

00:01:22.516 --> 00:01:25.726 A:middle
[ Cheering and Applause ]

00:01:26.226 --> 00:01:27.776 A:middle
It's the original App Store, the

00:01:27.776 --> 00:01:27.936 A:middle
OG.

00:01:27.936 --> 00:01:30.316 A:middle
It had been launched in July of

00:01:30.356 --> 00:01:33.436 A:middle
2008 with 500 apps.

00:01:33.986 --> 00:01:36.536 A:middle
And this is a little inside

00:01:36.956 --> 00:01:37.866 A:middle
story.

00:01:38.106 --> 00:01:39.066 A:middle
There were some prominent

00:01:39.066 --> 00:01:40.386 A:middle
executives at the company that

00:01:40.386 --> 00:01:41.516 A:middle
didn't think we'd have more than

00:01:41.516 --> 00:01:45.836 A:middle
a thousand apps in the App Store

00:01:46.266 --> 00:01:46.356 A:middle
ever.

00:01:46.356 --> 00:01:47.406 A:middle
The structure and the layout of

00:01:47.406 --> 00:01:48.826 A:middle
the store have largely remained

00:01:48.826 --> 00:01:49.276 A:middle
the same.

00:01:49.276 --> 00:01:50.246 A:middle
We changed things here and

00:01:50.246 --> 00:01:51.506 A:middle
there, but overall it's the same

00:01:51.506 --> 00:01:52.036 A:middle
store.

00:01:52.896 --> 00:01:53.636 A:middle
Tweaks have been made.

00:01:55.246 --> 00:01:56.336 A:middle
Well, nine years later there are

00:01:56.336 --> 00:01:58.056 A:middle
2.2 million apps in the store.

00:01:58.056 --> 00:01:59.516 A:middle
And it's transformed the way

00:01:59.516 --> 00:02:01.486 A:middle
software is bought and

00:02:01.486 --> 00:02:02.046 A:middle
distributed.

00:02:04.516 --> 00:02:07.826 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:02:08.326 --> 00:02:09.386 A:middle
It's hard to imagine a time

00:02:09.386 --> 00:02:10.106 A:middle
before Apps.

00:02:10.476 --> 00:02:11.906 A:middle
It's permeated every facet of

00:02:11.906 --> 00:02:13.176 A:middle
our lives from the way we travel

00:02:13.176 --> 00:02:14.296 A:middle
to the way we find love.

00:02:15.516 --> 00:02:18.066 A:middle
[ Laughter ]

00:02:18.566 --> 00:02:19.586 A:middle
And they've affected entire

00:02:19.586 --> 00:02:20.786 A:middle
industries as well.

00:02:21.466 --> 00:02:24.826 A:middle
From airline travel to

00:02:24.826 --> 00:02:26.676 A:middle
healthcare to gaming.

00:02:26.676 --> 00:02:31.496 A:middle
As well as the way we play

00:02:31.496 --> 00:02:31.916 A:middle
games.

00:02:31.916 --> 00:02:34.986 A:middle
You saw this scene of people in

00:02:34.986 --> 00:02:37.006 A:middle
Hong Kong playing Pokemon Go on

00:02:37.006 --> 00:02:37.466 A:middle
Monday.

00:02:37.756 --> 00:02:38.926 A:middle
And I think it's just bonkers.

00:02:38.926 --> 00:02:39.406 A:middle
I love it.

00:02:40.436 --> 00:02:41.846 A:middle
Well at this point in the

00:02:41.846 --> 00:02:44.826 A:middle
history of the App Store, we

00:02:44.826 --> 00:02:46.166 A:middle
pause to consider how we can

00:02:46.166 --> 00:02:46.876 A:middle
make it even better.

00:02:46.876 --> 00:02:47.926 A:middle
How we could redesign it from

00:02:47.926 --> 00:02:48.576 A:middle
the ground up.

00:02:49.726 --> 00:02:52.366 A:middle
And as we began doing that, we

00:02:52.366 --> 00:02:53.426 A:middle
realized it could serve a few

00:02:53.426 --> 00:02:54.026 A:middle
purposes.

00:02:54.566 --> 00:02:57.576 A:middle
One, we thought how can we give

00:02:57.576 --> 00:02:58.796 A:middle
customers a reason to come back

00:02:58.796 --> 00:02:59.226 A:middle
every day?

00:02:59.226 --> 00:03:00.326 A:middle
Make it a destination they'd

00:03:00.326 --> 00:03:02.156 A:middle
want to visit on a daily basis?

00:03:02.636 --> 00:03:04.976 A:middle
Second, we thought this was a

00:03:04.976 --> 00:03:06.296 A:middle
perfect time to double down on

00:03:06.296 --> 00:03:07.556 A:middle
the editorial curation that's

00:03:07.556 --> 00:03:08.486 A:middle
distinguished the App Store

00:03:08.486 --> 00:03:09.376 A:middle
since its inception.

00:03:10.916 --> 00:03:11.936 A:middle
And finally, we wanted to

00:03:11.936 --> 00:03:13.146 A:middle
reflect the significance the

00:03:13.146 --> 00:03:15.556 A:middle
games play in the App Store and

00:03:15.556 --> 00:03:16.916 A:middle
give both games and apps a

00:03:16.956 --> 00:03:17.776 A:middle
clearer focus.

00:03:18.356 --> 00:03:21.666 A:middle
At this stage, we began an

00:03:21.666 --> 00:03:23.756 A:middle
intense journey of redesigning

00:03:23.756 --> 00:03:24.836 A:middle
the store from the ground up.

00:03:26.726 --> 00:03:27.626 A:middle
To tell you more about the

00:03:27.626 --> 00:03:29.496 A:middle
process, I'm thrilled to hand it

00:03:29.496 --> 00:03:31.066 A:middle
over to Monika Gromek who led

00:03:31.066 --> 00:03:31.986 A:middle
these design efforts.

00:03:32.476 --> 00:03:32.786 A:middle
Monika.

00:03:33.516 --> 00:03:41.606 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:03:42.106 --> 00:03:43.286 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Thanks Pedraum, for letting

00:03:43.286 --> 00:03:44.566 A:middle
me out of the office once in a

00:03:44.566 --> 00:03:44.946 A:middle
while.

00:03:46.076 --> 00:03:47.276 A:middle
And thank you all for coming to

00:03:47.276 --> 00:03:47.946 A:middle
this session.

00:03:48.656 --> 00:03:50.196 A:middle
My name is Monika Gromek and I

00:03:50.196 --> 00:03:51.556 A:middle
lead the App Store design team

00:03:51.556 --> 00:03:52.096 A:middle
at Apple.

00:03:53.246 --> 00:03:54.806 A:middle
This redesign of the App Store

00:03:54.806 --> 00:03:57.436 A:middle
is so significant that we felt

00:03:57.436 --> 00:03:59.386 A:middle
it deserved a session dedicated

00:03:59.386 --> 00:04:00.256 A:middle
just to this one topic.

00:04:00.256 --> 00:04:02.106 A:middle
And hopefully by the end of it

00:04:02.106 --> 00:04:03.366 A:middle
you'll be much more familiar

00:04:03.716 --> 00:04:04.686 A:middle
with the changes that we're

00:04:04.686 --> 00:04:06.406 A:middle
making and all the new features

00:04:06.436 --> 00:04:07.416 A:middle
that we're introducing.

00:04:08.126 --> 00:04:09.706 A:middle
I am going to cover the major

00:04:09.706 --> 00:04:10.846 A:middle
parts of the redesign.

00:04:11.336 --> 00:04:12.946 A:middle
But I would like start with our

00:04:12.946 --> 00:04:14.576 A:middle
goals and the design process.

00:04:15.276 --> 00:04:18.086 A:middle
As Pedraum mentioned, the App

00:04:18.136 --> 00:04:19.696 A:middle
Store launched nine years ago.

00:04:20.546 --> 00:04:22.496 A:middle
And it's so hard to believe that

00:04:22.566 --> 00:04:23.596 A:middle
so much time has passed.

00:04:24.586 --> 00:04:26.526 A:middle
And we are incredibly proud of

00:04:26.526 --> 00:04:27.756 A:middle
what it has become.

00:04:28.096 --> 00:04:30.346 A:middle
And mostly, thanks to all of you

00:04:30.426 --> 00:04:31.816 A:middle
and the amazing apps and games

00:04:31.856 --> 00:04:33.156 A:middle
that you create every day.

00:04:34.636 --> 00:04:36.086 A:middle
So why the redesign?

00:04:37.646 --> 00:04:39.566 A:middle
Well, it was time for us to take

00:04:39.566 --> 00:04:41.636 A:middle
a long, hard look at the current

00:04:41.716 --> 00:04:43.576 A:middle
store and acknowledge its

00:04:43.576 --> 00:04:46.116 A:middle
limitations, as none of us could

00:04:46.116 --> 00:04:48.056 A:middle
have predicted its tremendous

00:04:48.056 --> 00:04:48.406 A:middle
growth.

00:04:50.066 --> 00:04:51.936 A:middle
So just like every other app and

00:04:51.936 --> 00:04:53.496 A:middle
game creator on the App Store,

00:04:53.996 --> 00:04:55.036 A:middle
we asked ourselves two

00:04:55.036 --> 00:04:57.766 A:middle
questions: What are our goals

00:04:57.766 --> 00:04:58.156 A:middle
now?

00:04:58.646 --> 00:05:00.206 A:middle
And how does the current design

00:05:00.236 --> 00:05:00.946 A:middle
support them?

00:05:03.016 --> 00:05:04.836 A:middle
For the new store, we touched

00:05:04.836 --> 00:05:07.056 A:middle
every single view and thought

00:05:07.056 --> 00:05:08.626 A:middle
hard about the structure of the

00:05:08.626 --> 00:05:08.786 A:middle
app.

00:05:09.916 --> 00:05:11.206 A:middle
Believe me, there were a lot of

00:05:11.206 --> 00:05:12.386 A:middle
options on the table.

00:05:13.286 --> 00:05:15.366 A:middle
We applied lessons from other

00:05:15.366 --> 00:05:17.696 A:middle
redesigns at Apple, but the

00:05:17.696 --> 00:05:20.036 A:middle
final design is unique to the

00:05:20.036 --> 00:05:20.606 A:middle
App Store.

00:05:22.036 --> 00:05:24.156 A:middle
The end result is a new sense of

00:05:24.226 --> 00:05:25.996 A:middle
clarity, a general

00:05:25.996 --> 00:05:28.156 A:middle
simplification of the app, and a

00:05:28.156 --> 00:05:29.726 A:middle
fresh take on editorial.

00:05:30.726 --> 00:05:32.526 A:middle
The new style of typography

00:05:33.136 --> 00:05:35.026 A:middle
helps establish hierarchy on the

00:05:35.026 --> 00:05:37.256 A:middle
pages and a sense of space.

00:05:38.156 --> 00:05:39.876 A:middle
It guides people throughout

00:05:39.876 --> 00:05:40.596 A:middle
their journey.

00:05:41.696 --> 00:05:43.436 A:middle
We've also removed extra layers

00:05:43.436 --> 00:05:45.546 A:middle
of UIs such as toggles to help

00:05:45.546 --> 00:05:48.106 A:middle
with the overall experience in

00:05:48.386 --> 00:05:50.426 A:middle
the App Store.

00:05:50.636 --> 00:05:51.726 A:middle
Let's take a look at our

00:05:51.726 --> 00:05:52.616 A:middle
redesign goals.

00:05:54.716 --> 00:05:55.986 A:middle
As you can see, these are

00:05:55.986 --> 00:05:58.166 A:middle
exactly the same as the ones you

00:05:58.166 --> 00:05:59.536 A:middle
heard a few minutes ago.

00:06:01.046 --> 00:06:03.386 A:middle
This alignment of goals helped

00:06:03.386 --> 00:06:04.836 A:middle
us create a product that's

00:06:04.886 --> 00:06:06.646 A:middle
integrated, fluid and also

00:06:06.646 --> 00:06:07.246 A:middle
beautiful.

00:06:08.816 --> 00:06:10.706 A:middle
We did add one goal from the

00:06:10.706 --> 00:06:11.526 A:middle
design side.

00:06:13.116 --> 00:06:14.436 A:middle
And that is clarity and

00:06:14.436 --> 00:06:15.416 A:middle
simplification.

00:06:16.256 --> 00:06:17.316 A:middle
And it's probably the most

00:06:17.316 --> 00:06:18.116 A:middle
important goal.

00:06:18.296 --> 00:06:19.696 A:middle
And I will expand on it later.

00:06:19.696 --> 00:06:24.226 A:middle
I want to start by talking about

00:06:24.226 --> 00:06:25.416 A:middle
the App Store as a daily

00:06:25.416 --> 00:06:27.386 A:middle
destination and the editorial

00:06:27.386 --> 00:06:28.676 A:middle
voice on the App Store, as the

00:06:28.676 --> 00:06:30.726 A:middle
two goals are very closely

00:06:30.726 --> 00:06:31.196 A:middle
related.

00:06:32.686 --> 00:06:34.166 A:middle
To do that, I want to bring up

00:06:34.166 --> 00:06:34.976 A:middle
the Today view.

00:06:35.536 --> 00:06:36.666 A:middle
You saw it in the Monday

00:06:36.766 --> 00:06:37.216 A:middle
keynote.

00:06:38.106 --> 00:06:40.066 A:middle
But let's take a closer look.

00:06:40.646 --> 00:06:42.746 A:middle
It all starts with the Today

00:06:42.746 --> 00:06:42.856 A:middle
tab.

00:06:43.676 --> 00:06:45.366 A:middle
This is our new home for the App

00:06:45.526 --> 00:06:45.756 A:middle
Store.

00:06:46.226 --> 00:06:47.526 A:middle
This is where we can share our

00:06:47.526 --> 00:06:49.176 A:middle
passion for apps and games and

00:06:49.206 --> 00:06:50.436 A:middle
celebrate all of you, the

00:06:50.436 --> 00:06:51.066 A:middle
creators.

00:06:52.386 --> 00:06:53.816 A:middle
This is where you can come and

00:06:53.816 --> 00:06:55.826 A:middle
learn our editorial perspective

00:06:55.826 --> 00:06:57.266 A:middle
on the world of apps and games.

00:06:57.806 --> 00:06:59.166 A:middle
This view is a dynamic,

00:06:59.166 --> 00:07:00.976 A:middle
ever-changing platform that

00:07:00.976 --> 00:07:02.366 A:middle
allows us to feature your

00:07:02.366 --> 00:07:04.256 A:middle
products in a very different

00:07:04.256 --> 00:07:05.886 A:middle
light than ever before.

00:07:06.556 --> 00:07:10.446 A:middle
We designed it as a series of

00:07:10.506 --> 00:07:14.286 A:middle
cards that update daily and

00:07:14.286 --> 00:07:15.946 A:middle
allow us to celebrate your apps

00:07:15.946 --> 00:07:17.456 A:middle
and games by telling stories.

00:07:18.406 --> 00:07:20.006 A:middle
We've had this desire to tell

00:07:20.066 --> 00:07:22.156 A:middle
stories for a long time now but

00:07:22.156 --> 00:07:23.596 A:middle
haven't been able to do it in a

00:07:23.596 --> 00:07:25.366 A:middle
meaningful and engaging way.

00:07:26.006 --> 00:07:27.356 A:middle
But this is all changing now

00:07:27.356 --> 00:07:28.426 A:middle
with the Today tab.

00:07:29.666 --> 00:07:31.136 A:middle
What you see here is our video

00:07:31.136 --> 00:07:31.466 A:middle
card.

00:07:32.396 --> 00:07:34.236 A:middle
We can highlight your app and

00:07:34.236 --> 00:07:36.076 A:middle
game previews and our

00:07:36.076 --> 00:07:38.606 A:middle
editorially-created videos.

00:07:39.576 --> 00:07:41.586 A:middle
We will be providing helpful

00:07:41.586 --> 00:07:43.796 A:middle
tips and tricks as seen in this

00:07:43.796 --> 00:07:45.066 A:middle
example for VSCO.

00:07:45.706 --> 00:07:48.186 A:middle
And we will be nominating an App

00:07:48.356 --> 00:07:49.786 A:middle
of the Day and a Game of the

00:07:49.786 --> 00:07:50.106 A:middle
Day.

00:07:50.756 --> 00:07:55.666 A:middle
And we will also be sharing our

00:07:55.666 --> 00:07:56.766 A:middle
curated collections.

00:07:57.446 --> 00:07:58.696 A:middle
Some of you might be familiar

00:07:58.696 --> 00:08:00.066 A:middle
with our collections, as we've

00:08:00.066 --> 00:08:01.586 A:middle
been creating them for years,

00:08:02.266 --> 00:08:03.426 A:middle
but haven't had a way to

00:08:03.426 --> 00:08:04.926 A:middle
highlight them in a predictable

00:08:04.926 --> 00:08:05.726 A:middle
way in our UI.

00:08:06.576 --> 00:08:08.006 A:middle
But again, this is different now

00:08:08.006 --> 00:08:09.406 A:middle
with the Today tab and these

00:08:09.456 --> 00:08:09.806 A:middle
cards.

00:08:11.256 --> 00:08:12.596 A:middle
We spent a lot of time thinking

00:08:12.596 --> 00:08:14.306 A:middle
about how to best showcase your

00:08:14.526 --> 00:08:15.826 A:middle
apps and games in this view.

00:08:17.326 --> 00:08:18.696 A:middle
It was important to us that it

00:08:18.696 --> 00:08:20.766 A:middle
looked beautiful, so we spent a

00:08:20.766 --> 00:08:22.816 A:middle
lot of time thinking about every

00:08:22.816 --> 00:08:25.176 A:middle
single detail.

00:08:25.336 --> 00:08:26.676 A:middle
Everything kept us up at night

00:08:26.766 --> 00:08:28.886 A:middle
for months, be it typography,

00:08:28.886 --> 00:08:30.536 A:middle
layout, transitions and

00:08:30.536 --> 00:08:31.246 A:middle
animations.

00:08:31.966 --> 00:08:35.626 A:middle
Each card is an entry point for

00:08:35.626 --> 00:08:36.736 A:middle
a deeper discovery.

00:08:37.916 --> 00:08:39.336 A:middle
And we also hope to give you

00:08:39.336 --> 00:08:40.946 A:middle
some context into why you should

00:08:40.946 --> 00:08:42.536 A:middle
tap in and check out that story.

00:08:44.176 --> 00:08:45.686 A:middle
At any given point we will give

00:08:45.686 --> 00:08:47.326 A:middle
you up to seven days' worth of

00:08:47.366 --> 00:08:47.936 A:middle
content.

00:08:47.996 --> 00:08:50.086 A:middle
So if you miss a day or two, you

00:08:50.086 --> 00:08:51.556 A:middle
can come back and find it later.

00:08:52.876 --> 00:08:57.976 A:middle
Just look for the date markers.

00:08:58.746 --> 00:09:00.656 A:middle
We also included animations on

00:09:00.656 --> 00:09:02.216 A:middle
some of these cards to make them

00:09:02.216 --> 00:09:02.926 A:middle
come to life.

00:09:03.586 --> 00:09:04.396 A:middle
You've already seen the

00:09:04.476 --> 00:09:05.506 A:middle
auto-playing video.

00:09:05.756 --> 00:09:06.786 A:middle
But we hope to bring more

00:09:06.786 --> 00:09:09.616 A:middle
movement into this view.

00:09:10.176 --> 00:09:11.656 A:middle
Twelve cards will be ready for

00:09:11.656 --> 00:09:12.116 A:middle
launch.

00:09:13.286 --> 00:09:15.066 A:middle
We needed a variety to keep

00:09:15.066 --> 00:09:15.996 A:middle
things interesting.

00:09:16.766 --> 00:09:18.346 A:middle
But also to be able to tell

00:09:18.346 --> 00:09:19.626 A:middle
diverse type of stories.

00:09:20.316 --> 00:09:21.756 A:middle
And each one of these cards

00:09:21.756 --> 00:09:23.506 A:middle
allows us to tell a story in a

00:09:23.506 --> 00:09:24.236 A:middle
different way.

00:09:25.946 --> 00:09:27.406 A:middle
It was also important that these

00:09:27.456 --> 00:09:29.106 A:middle
cards look good together and

00:09:29.106 --> 00:09:30.016 A:middle
work as a system.

00:09:31.266 --> 00:09:33.036 A:middle
The order in which they appear

00:09:33.036 --> 00:09:35.376 A:middle
might be different, so what you

00:09:35.426 --> 00:09:36.746 A:middle
see one day might be very

00:09:36.746 --> 00:09:38.266 A:middle
different from what you will see

00:09:38.266 --> 00:09:39.436 A:middle
tomorrow, for example.

00:09:40.516 --> 00:09:42.586 A:middle
But, there's a lot of thought

00:09:42.586 --> 00:09:44.156 A:middle
that goes into creating these

00:09:44.556 --> 00:09:46.326 A:middle
every single day around the

00:09:46.326 --> 00:09:46.696 A:middle
world.

00:09:47.566 --> 00:09:48.876 A:middle
We haven't done this before.

00:09:48.936 --> 00:09:50.876 A:middle
And believe me, it keeps things

00:09:50.876 --> 00:09:52.776 A:middle
interesting, even at Apple.

00:09:53.646 --> 00:09:55.196 A:middle
I do want to share one other

00:09:55.196 --> 00:09:57.096 A:middle
thing about the cards, which is

00:09:57.376 --> 00:09:59.166 A:middle
personally important to me.

00:09:59.696 --> 00:10:01.726 A:middle
That this view is relevant world

00:10:01.726 --> 00:10:02.106 A:middle
wide.

00:10:03.276 --> 00:10:05.076 A:middle
So all this content will be

00:10:05.076 --> 00:10:07.356 A:middle
localized and culturally aware

00:10:07.986 --> 00:10:09.326 A:middle
in all our territories.

00:10:10.026 --> 00:10:14.646 A:middle
Let's take a closer look at one

00:10:14.646 --> 00:10:15.376 A:middle
of these stories.

00:10:16.496 --> 00:10:18.256 A:middle
It focuses on the fact that

00:10:18.256 --> 00:10:20.126 A:middle
behind every app there is a

00:10:20.126 --> 00:10:23.276 A:middle
story of who made it, what

00:10:23.276 --> 00:10:25.376 A:middle
motivated them, and how it was

00:10:25.406 --> 00:10:25.816 A:middle
made.

00:10:26.786 --> 00:10:28.676 A:middle
It celebrates you and your apps

00:10:28.676 --> 00:10:29.176 A:middle
and games.

00:10:30.226 --> 00:10:31.000 A:middle
Let's dive in.

00:10:35.796 --> 00:10:38.016 A:middle
The transition into this story

00:10:38.016 --> 00:10:39.396 A:middle
is smooth and fluid.

00:10:39.396 --> 00:10:41.846 A:middle
And it's also easy to go back

00:10:41.846 --> 00:10:42.916 A:middle
out to the Today view.

00:10:42.956 --> 00:10:44.646 A:middle
Simply tap on the X button or

00:10:44.646 --> 00:10:46.116 A:middle
swipe down on the article.

00:10:47.816 --> 00:10:49.706 A:middle
The stories are engaging and

00:10:49.706 --> 00:10:50.366 A:middle
informative.

00:10:51.046 --> 00:10:53.036 A:middle
Smokey, who leads our editorial

00:10:53.036 --> 00:10:54.566 A:middle
team, will come on stage in a

00:10:54.566 --> 00:10:55.956 A:middle
bit and talk to you about it in

00:10:55.956 --> 00:10:56.586 A:middle
more detail.

00:10:57.136 --> 00:10:58.556 A:middle
But I want to highlight a few

00:10:58.636 --> 00:10:59.966 A:middle
elements of these stories from

00:10:59.966 --> 00:11:01.066 A:middle
the design perspective.

00:11:04.336 --> 00:11:06.776 A:middle
We're letting the elements of

00:11:06.776 --> 00:11:09.006 A:middle
the stories define the space,

00:11:09.416 --> 00:11:11.086 A:middle
allowing them to breathe and

00:11:11.086 --> 00:11:12.466 A:middle
convey our perspective.

00:11:14.296 --> 00:11:17.426 A:middle
The videos let us engage with

00:11:17.426 --> 00:11:18.976 A:middle
the viewer like we've never been

00:11:18.976 --> 00:11:20.076 A:middle
able to do before.

00:11:20.816 --> 00:11:24.936 A:middle
And each story is a series of

00:11:24.936 --> 00:11:27.136 A:middle
modules defined by our design

00:11:27.196 --> 00:11:28.386 A:middle
and editorial teams.

00:11:29.096 --> 00:11:32.376 A:middle
We also hope that you will share

00:11:32.376 --> 00:11:33.856 A:middle
these stories with one another

00:11:34.166 --> 00:11:36.206 A:middle
and enjoy them as much as we do.

00:11:38.036 --> 00:11:39.066 A:middle
The modules allow for

00:11:39.066 --> 00:11:40.686 A:middle
flexibility in terms of how

00:11:40.686 --> 00:11:41.886 A:middle
these stories are built.

00:11:43.356 --> 00:11:44.706 A:middle
But they also keep things

00:11:44.766 --> 00:11:46.826 A:middle
consistent from the design side.

00:11:48.656 --> 00:11:50.476 A:middle
So we have this common language

00:11:50.476 --> 00:11:51.926 A:middle
that ties them all together,

00:11:51.926 --> 00:11:53.716 A:middle
making it easier for people to

00:11:53.716 --> 00:11:57.486 A:middle
experience that content.

00:11:58.086 --> 00:11:59.436 A:middle
It's also worth mentioning that

00:11:59.486 --> 00:12:00.876 A:middle
for the first time ever this

00:12:00.876 --> 00:12:02.586 A:middle
editorial content will be

00:12:02.586 --> 00:12:03.216 A:middle
searchable.

00:12:03.736 --> 00:12:05.116 A:middle
We've actually never had that in

00:12:05.116 --> 00:12:05.656 A:middle
the App Store.

00:12:05.656 --> 00:12:07.086 A:middle
And we are incredibly excited

00:12:07.086 --> 00:12:08.866 A:middle
about this.

00:12:09.131 --> 00:12:11.131 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:12:11.246 --> 00:12:11.706 A:middle
Absolutely.

00:12:11.706 --> 00:12:15.876 A:middle
So if you miss a day, or if you

00:12:15.876 --> 00:12:17.706 A:middle
miss some of this content, be it

00:12:17.706 --> 00:12:19.126 A:middle
in the Today tab or any other

00:12:19.196 --> 00:12:20.216 A:middle
place in the App Store, you can

00:12:20.246 --> 00:12:21.456 A:middle
simply search for it later.

00:12:22.256 --> 00:12:23.466 A:middle
It will be featured on the

00:12:23.466 --> 00:12:25.086 A:middle
product page as well for that

00:12:25.276 --> 00:12:25.846 A:middle
app or game.

00:12:26.416 --> 00:12:29.986 A:middle
And of course, the Today tab

00:12:30.066 --> 00:12:32.726 A:middle
will be part of this App Store

00:12:33.996 --> 00:12:35.366 A:middle
on the iPad.

00:12:35.366 --> 00:12:36.526 A:middle
And that is the Today view.

00:12:36.526 --> 00:12:38.466 A:middle
We're incredibly excited about

00:12:38.466 --> 00:12:39.916 A:middle
how it looks and how it works.

00:12:39.996 --> 00:12:41.996 A:middle
But more importantly, about the

00:12:41.996 --> 00:12:44.316 A:middle
type of stories it will allow us

00:12:44.376 --> 00:12:46.076 A:middle
to tell you every single day.

00:12:46.706 --> 00:12:50.986 A:middle
Let's talk about games next.

00:12:52.156 --> 00:12:54.136 A:middle
Games have been always a huge

00:12:54.186 --> 00:12:55.226 A:middle
part of the App Store.

00:12:56.866 --> 00:12:58.406 A:middle
But up to this point always

00:12:58.446 --> 00:13:00.526 A:middle
mixed with apps throughout our

00:13:00.586 --> 00:13:01.806 A:middle
editorial and charts.

00:13:03.286 --> 00:13:05.036 A:middle
Because of their importance and

00:13:05.036 --> 00:13:07.656 A:middle
success, we're dedicating a home

00:13:07.656 --> 00:13:09.956 A:middle
just for games in the App Store.

00:13:10.006 --> 00:13:12.326 A:middle
And that is the new Games tab.

00:13:13.206 --> 00:13:14.906 A:middle
It is more than a tab.

00:13:15.426 --> 00:13:17.256 A:middle
We're striving to create the

00:13:17.256 --> 00:13:19.536 A:middle
best, world's best game store.

00:13:20.086 --> 00:13:22.116 A:middle
Full of amazing content that

00:13:22.116 --> 00:13:23.206 A:middle
people are going to love.

00:13:24.236 --> 00:13:26.056 A:middle
The top of the page allows for

00:13:26.776 --> 00:13:28.976 A:middle
space for more stories to be

00:13:28.976 --> 00:13:32.596 A:middle
dedicated just to games or new

00:13:32.596 --> 00:13:33.156 A:middle
releases.

00:13:33.896 --> 00:13:36.896 A:middle
And with more focus on videos,

00:13:36.946 --> 00:13:39.436 A:middle
people will be able to discover

00:13:39.616 --> 00:13:41.066 A:middle
games much more quickly and

00:13:41.066 --> 00:13:42.316 A:middle
engage with them almost

00:13:42.316 --> 00:13:42.976 A:middle
immediately.

00:13:43.576 --> 00:13:48.456 A:middle
The split between apps and games

00:13:48.906 --> 00:13:50.666 A:middle
also allowed us to make charts

00:13:50.716 --> 00:13:51.986 A:middle
much more relevant in the App

00:13:52.186 --> 00:13:52.406 A:middle
Store.

00:13:53.766 --> 00:13:55.706 A:middle
So, the charts that you're

00:13:55.706 --> 00:13:57.386 A:middle
seeing are specifically

00:13:57.386 --> 00:13:58.386 A:middle
dedicated to games.

00:13:58.386 --> 00:14:00.036 A:middle
And the same is true for apps.

00:14:00.326 --> 00:14:01.736 A:middle
They will not be mixed in.

00:14:02.286 --> 00:14:05.116 A:middle
We think this will actually make

00:14:05.116 --> 00:14:06.776 A:middle
it a lot easier to find what's

00:14:06.816 --> 00:14:10.386 A:middle
popular on the App Store.

00:14:10.776 --> 00:14:12.436 A:middle
The same is true of categories.

00:14:13.126 --> 00:14:14.566 A:middle
As some of you may know, games

00:14:14.566 --> 00:14:16.006 A:middle
was just one of the categories

00:14:16.006 --> 00:14:16.896 A:middle
in the previous store.

00:14:17.536 --> 00:14:19.046 A:middle
Unfortunately, what it meant is

00:14:19.046 --> 00:14:20.696 A:middle
that all the subcategories were

00:14:20.696 --> 00:14:22.406 A:middle
harder to find and all that

00:14:22.606 --> 00:14:23.866 A:middle
content was hidden.

00:14:24.986 --> 00:14:28.536 A:middle
But creating a tab dedicated for

00:14:28.536 --> 00:14:30.396 A:middle
games, we can take all those

00:14:30.436 --> 00:14:32.156 A:middle
categories and put them on the

00:14:32.156 --> 00:14:34.806 A:middle
top level, making browsing by

00:14:34.806 --> 00:14:36.886 A:middle
categories a lot easier and that

00:14:36.886 --> 00:14:39.406 A:middle
content a lot easier to find.

00:14:39.906 --> 00:14:43.386 A:middle
Throughout the App Store will

00:14:43.386 --> 00:14:44.986 A:middle
also be providing more context

00:14:45.666 --> 00:14:47.206 A:middle
for any particular app or game.

00:14:47.466 --> 00:14:48.896 A:middle
The App Store is no longer just

00:14:50.276 --> 00:14:51.536 A:middle
app icons.

00:14:51.706 --> 00:14:54.166 A:middle
We want to help people find what

00:14:54.166 --> 00:14:55.716 A:middle
they're looking for and make the

00:14:55.716 --> 00:14:56.856 A:middle
right download choices.

00:14:57.866 --> 00:14:59.846 A:middle
The context can come from your

00:14:59.846 --> 00:15:01.326 A:middle
subtitles that you will be

00:15:01.326 --> 00:15:02.696 A:middle
providing for your apps.

00:15:03.636 --> 00:15:05.086 A:middle
And these subtitles are as

00:15:05.086 --> 00:15:06.586 A:middle
important as your app names

00:15:06.636 --> 00:15:07.046 A:middle
today.

00:15:08.366 --> 00:15:09.556 A:middle
And again, it's to provide

00:15:09.556 --> 00:15:11.036 A:middle
people with more information

00:15:11.036 --> 00:15:12.226 A:middle
about your app and game.

00:15:12.836 --> 00:15:16.466 A:middle
The context can also come from

00:15:16.466 --> 00:15:17.646 A:middle
the editorial team.

00:15:18.026 --> 00:15:19.326 A:middle
And you will see more and more

00:15:19.326 --> 00:15:23.266 A:middle
of it throughout the App Store.

00:15:23.476 --> 00:15:24.956 A:middle
And that is the new Games tab.

00:15:25.216 --> 00:15:26.636 A:middle
We're incredibly excited about

00:15:26.636 --> 00:15:28.176 A:middle
having a dedicated home for

00:15:28.176 --> 00:15:28.546 A:middle
games.

00:15:29.456 --> 00:15:30.766 A:middle
Before we move on, I just wanted

00:15:30.766 --> 00:15:32.256 A:middle
to highlight a small but playful

00:15:32.256 --> 00:15:33.916 A:middle
detail about the Games tab.

00:15:34.756 --> 00:15:38.246 A:middle
Icon. The shape of the rocket is

00:15:38.246 --> 00:15:39.786 A:middle
actually based on the leaf from

00:15:39.786 --> 00:15:40.536 A:middle
the Apple logo.

00:15:41.326 --> 00:15:42.276 A:middle
We thought some of you might

00:15:42.336 --> 00:15:43.186 A:middle
find it interesting.

00:15:43.756 --> 00:15:46.346 A:middle
In addition to the Games tab,

00:15:46.666 --> 00:15:48.516 A:middle
we're also creating a new home

00:15:48.516 --> 00:15:49.936 A:middle
for apps.

00:15:51.136 --> 00:15:53.086 A:middle
All the amazing content that you

00:15:53.136 --> 00:15:54.916 A:middle
saw for the Games tab will also

00:15:54.916 --> 00:15:56.746 A:middle
be available in the Apps tab.

00:15:57.856 --> 00:15:59.206 A:middle
From the design perspective

00:15:59.206 --> 00:16:00.486 A:middle
there was always this tension

00:16:00.486 --> 00:16:01.626 A:middle
between apps and games.

00:16:01.896 --> 00:16:03.546 A:middle
And we felt it was a problem we

00:16:03.546 --> 00:16:05.606 A:middle
needed to solve, as apps are

00:16:05.606 --> 00:16:07.766 A:middle
incredibly important and have a

00:16:07.766 --> 00:16:10.326 A:middle
huge impact on how we live our

00:16:10.456 --> 00:16:10.596 A:middle
lives.

00:16:12.126 --> 00:16:13.686 A:middle
By splitting games and apps we

00:16:13.686 --> 00:16:15.186 A:middle
can give both of them the

00:16:15.186 --> 00:16:18.836 A:middle
attention they deserve.

00:16:18.996 --> 00:16:20.996 A:middle
And finding new apps will be so

00:16:20.996 --> 00:16:23.176 A:middle
much easier with App Previews,

00:16:23.726 --> 00:16:25.206 A:middle
as you see in this example for

00:16:25.206 --> 00:16:25.676 A:middle
Mammals.

00:16:26.366 --> 00:16:29.486 A:middle
What you will see in both tabs

00:16:29.726 --> 00:16:30.756 A:middle
are in-app purchases.

00:16:31.696 --> 00:16:33.276 A:middle
Up to this point they had a very

00:16:33.276 --> 00:16:34.426 A:middle
limited presence in the App

00:16:34.626 --> 00:16:34.836 A:middle
Store.

00:16:36.266 --> 00:16:37.666 A:middle
But we're changing it completely

00:16:37.666 --> 00:16:38.746 A:middle
with this redesign.

00:16:39.956 --> 00:16:40.906 A:middle
They will be much more

00:16:40.906 --> 00:16:42.716 A:middle
accessible and discoverable

00:16:42.716 --> 00:16:46.236 A:middle
throughout the App Store.

00:16:46.456 --> 00:16:47.636 A:middle
You will see them on the Today

00:16:47.636 --> 00:16:47.746 A:middle
tab.

00:16:48.216 --> 00:16:49.586 A:middle
We actually designed a card

00:16:49.646 --> 00:16:50.656 A:middle
specifically for in-app

00:16:50.716 --> 00:16:51.066 A:middle
purchases.

00:16:51.066 --> 00:16:53.146 A:middle
They will be highlighted on the

00:16:53.146 --> 00:16:54.176 A:middle
Apps and Games tab.

00:16:54.306 --> 00:16:56.126 A:middle
And they will be searchable.

00:16:57.096 --> 00:16:58.626 A:middle
They will also be featured by

00:16:58.756 --> 00:17:00.186 A:middle
you on your product pages.

00:17:00.506 --> 00:17:01.746 A:middle
It is a complete story.

00:17:02.906 --> 00:17:04.106 A:middle
What's probably even more

00:17:04.106 --> 00:17:06.656 A:middle
important, how easy it is to get

00:17:06.886 --> 00:17:08.476 A:middle
the in-app purchases, especially

00:17:08.476 --> 00:17:10.446 A:middle
if you have the app installed on

00:17:10.446 --> 00:17:10.986 A:middle
your own device.

00:17:11.656 --> 00:17:12.576 A:middle
I'm going to start with the

00:17:12.576 --> 00:17:14.036 A:middle
Today tab and the card

00:17:14.426 --> 00:17:16.206 A:middle
specifically designed for the

00:17:16.206 --> 00:17:16.856 A:middle
in-app purchases.

00:17:16.856 --> 00:17:18.846 A:middle
I'm going to tap on the Buy

00:17:18.846 --> 00:17:19.336 A:middle
button.

00:17:20.626 --> 00:17:21.466 A:middle
The app will open.

00:17:21.466 --> 00:17:24.876 A:middle
And the purchase sheet will come

00:17:26.226 --> 00:17:26.316 A:middle
up.

00:17:26.316 --> 00:17:28.316 A:middle
I can confirm with Touch ID and

00:17:28.376 --> 00:17:29.376 A:middle
I'm done.

00:17:29.496 --> 00:17:31.726 A:middle
It's simple and direct.

00:17:32.516 --> 00:17:37.716 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:17:38.216 --> 00:17:39.446 A:middle
When designing the visual

00:17:39.446 --> 00:17:40.766 A:middle
treatment for in-app purchases,

00:17:40.766 --> 00:17:42.856 A:middle
it was important to us that

00:17:42.856 --> 00:17:44.216 A:middle
these wouldn't be confused for

00:17:44.216 --> 00:17:45.296 A:middle
being app icons.

00:17:46.296 --> 00:17:47.816 A:middle
We started with the image that

00:17:47.816 --> 00:17:48.966 A:middle
you will be providing for

00:17:48.966 --> 00:17:50.396 A:middle
featuring your in-app purchases.

00:17:50.396 --> 00:17:53.306 A:middle
And we added a framing system

00:17:53.566 --> 00:17:54.966 A:middle
that helps convey what these

00:17:54.966 --> 00:17:57.096 A:middle
truly are, in addition to an app

00:17:57.096 --> 00:17:57.726 A:middle
or a game.

00:17:58.566 --> 00:18:00.086 A:middle
And the [inaudible] helps

00:18:00.126 --> 00:18:03.256 A:middle
communicate that as well.

00:18:03.786 --> 00:18:05.926 A:middle
The curve of the frame actually

00:18:05.926 --> 00:18:07.156 A:middle
follows the shape of the app

00:18:07.346 --> 00:18:09.056 A:middle
icons on the App Store today.

00:18:10.006 --> 00:18:11.286 A:middle
And the way we think of in-app

00:18:11.336 --> 00:18:13.106 A:middle
purchases is that they are the

00:18:13.186 --> 00:18:15.026 A:middle
smaller part of the larger

00:18:15.076 --> 00:18:18.846 A:middle
piece, which is the app itself.

00:18:19.856 --> 00:18:21.486 A:middle
It was also still important to

00:18:21.486 --> 00:18:23.076 A:middle
us to keep that connection

00:18:23.286 --> 00:18:24.676 A:middle
between the in-app purchase and

00:18:24.676 --> 00:18:25.426 A:middle
the parent app.

00:18:27.026 --> 00:18:28.726 A:middle
So we added the app icon in the

00:18:28.726 --> 00:18:30.806 A:middle
lower left corner, again for

00:18:30.806 --> 00:18:31.536 A:middle
more context.

00:18:32.346 --> 00:18:34.756 A:middle
If you would like to feature

00:18:34.756 --> 00:18:36.866 A:middle
your in-app purchases on a

00:18:36.866 --> 00:18:38.466 A:middle
store, you will need to submit

00:18:38.466 --> 00:18:40.226 A:middle
an image for every single one of

00:18:40.226 --> 00:18:41.266 A:middle
your in-app purchases.

00:18:42.216 --> 00:18:43.726 A:middle
It needs to be a custom design

00:18:44.006 --> 00:18:46.176 A:middle
asset that helps describe what

00:18:46.176 --> 00:18:47.556 A:middle
your in-app purchase is about.

00:18:48.416 --> 00:18:49.876 A:middle
It should not be a screen shot

00:18:49.926 --> 00:18:52.136 A:middle
from your app or an app icon.

00:18:52.776 --> 00:18:57.456 A:middle
The last goal, clarity and

00:18:57.456 --> 00:18:59.766 A:middle
simplification, is also the most

00:18:59.766 --> 00:19:01.036 A:middle
important, like I mentioned

00:19:01.296 --> 00:19:02.426 A:middle
earlier, from the design

00:19:02.426 --> 00:19:03.056 A:middle
perspective.

00:19:04.326 --> 00:19:05.406 A:middle
It also had the biggest

00:19:05.406 --> 00:19:06.876 A:middle
influence on the entire

00:19:06.926 --> 00:19:07.576 A:middle
redesign.

00:19:08.916 --> 00:19:10.576 A:middle
When designing our products, we

00:19:10.576 --> 00:19:13.046 A:middle
constantly ask ourselves: Is

00:19:13.046 --> 00:19:13.876 A:middle
this simple enough?

00:19:14.256 --> 00:19:15.886 A:middle
Is this clear to everyone?

