00:27:40.556 --> 00:27:41.486 A:middle
First it was, "We tell

00:27:41.486 --> 00:27:42.536 A:middle
interesting stories."

00:27:42.886 --> 00:27:44.696 A:middle
Then it was, "We tell insanely

00:27:44.926 --> 00:27:45.986 A:middle
interesting stories."

00:27:46.196 --> 00:27:47.356 A:middle
And this is where we landed,

00:27:47.416 --> 00:27:48.986 A:middle
"Interesting and important

00:27:48.986 --> 00:27:49.356 A:middle
stories."

00:27:49.356 --> 00:27:51.476 A:middle
Now, for sure, not every single

00:27:51.476 --> 00:27:53.486 A:middle
story on Today is going to be

00:27:53.486 --> 00:27:54.736 A:middle
super, super important.

00:27:55.056 --> 00:27:56.156 A:middle
But we're going to try really,

00:27:56.156 --> 00:27:57.456 A:middle
really hard to make sure that

00:27:57.456 --> 00:27:59.316 A:middle
they are very interesting.

00:27:59.316 --> 00:28:01.466 A:middle
They key for us is that us being

00:28:01.466 --> 00:28:02.636 A:middle
able to say that this app is

00:28:02.636 --> 00:28:04.536 A:middle
great is no longer enough.

00:28:04.996 --> 00:28:06.706 A:middle
In the current app store, that's

00:28:06.706 --> 00:28:07.596 A:middle
what we say.

00:28:07.596 --> 00:28:09.206 A:middle
And we feature and promote those

00:28:09.206 --> 00:28:09.516 A:middle
apps.

00:28:09.906 --> 00:28:11.486 A:middle
In our new design, newly

00:28:11.486 --> 00:28:12.896 A:middle
designed App Store, we will say

00:28:12.896 --> 00:28:14.146 A:middle
that app is great, but then

00:28:14.146 --> 00:28:16.786 A:middle
explain why we believe it is to

00:28:16.786 --> 00:28:17.576 A:middle
our customers.

00:28:17.876 --> 00:28:18.636 A:middle
We're here to provide

00:28:18.736 --> 00:28:20.396 A:middle
thought-provoking ideas and

00:28:20.396 --> 00:28:21.956 A:middle
really offer that context.

00:28:21.956 --> 00:28:25.216 A:middle
Our fifth and last principle is

00:28:25.216 --> 00:28:27.966 A:middle
we deliver a fresh and

00:28:27.966 --> 00:28:29.016 A:middle
unexpected take.

00:28:29.016 --> 00:28:30.326 A:middle
You know, the world of apps is

00:28:30.326 --> 00:28:31.956 A:middle
moving at a ridiculous speed.

00:28:32.406 --> 00:28:34.856 A:middle
It is our job, we believe, to

00:28:34.856 --> 00:28:36.606 A:middle
reflect that innovative culture.

00:28:36.606 --> 00:28:37.876 A:middle
You guys are pushing the world

00:28:37.876 --> 00:28:38.286 A:middle
ahead.

00:28:38.536 --> 00:28:40.146 A:middle
All of you are shaping our lives

00:28:40.436 --> 00:28:41.706 A:middle
with what you create.

00:28:42.156 --> 00:28:44.086 A:middle
And often you've changed things

00:28:44.086 --> 00:28:45.196 A:middle
in ways that are totally

00:28:45.196 --> 00:28:45.876 A:middle
unexpected.

00:28:45.876 --> 00:28:47.266 A:middle
So, we want to try to keep up

00:28:47.266 --> 00:28:47.706 A:middle
with you.

00:28:48.176 --> 00:28:49.626 A:middle
Keep up with that speed.

00:28:49.826 --> 00:28:51.086 A:middle
And for us, we kind of call this

00:28:51.086 --> 00:28:53.196 A:middle
our "the crazy ones" principles.

00:28:53.276 --> 00:28:54.876 A:middle
A fresh and unexpected take.

00:28:55.406 --> 00:28:57.906 A:middle
So these five principles all

00:28:57.906 --> 00:28:59.326 A:middle
together: We celebrate apps.

00:28:59.326 --> 00:29:00.636 A:middle
We are the voice of the App

00:29:00.636 --> 00:29:01.196 A:middle
Store.

00:29:01.496 --> 00:29:03.006 A:middle
We offer independent insights.

00:29:03.006 --> 00:29:03.976 A:middle
We tell interesting and

00:29:03.976 --> 00:29:04.936 A:middle
important stories.

00:29:05.166 --> 00:29:06.306 A:middle
And we deliver a fresh and

00:29:06.306 --> 00:29:07.186 A:middle
unexpected take.

00:29:07.386 --> 00:29:09.786 A:middle
When we do all this, if around

00:29:09.786 --> 00:29:11.506 A:middle
the world we abide by these

00:29:11.546 --> 00:29:13.436 A:middle
principles, then hopefully the

00:29:13.436 --> 00:29:15.066 A:middle
Today tab and the whole new App

00:29:15.066 --> 00:29:16.936 A:middle
Store become a pretty fabulous

00:29:16.936 --> 00:29:18.956 A:middle
document of app culture.

00:29:19.826 --> 00:29:21.246 A:middle
And for us at the App Store, app

00:29:21.276 --> 00:29:22.716 A:middle
culture in almost every single

00:29:22.716 --> 00:29:24.856 A:middle
way is culture.

00:29:25.456 --> 00:29:27.166 A:middle
All right.

00:29:27.266 --> 00:29:29.666 A:middle
The new tabs: Today, Games, and

00:29:29.666 --> 00:29:30.186 A:middle
Apps.

00:29:30.426 --> 00:29:31.806 A:middle
Each of these tabs have the same

00:29:31.806 --> 00:29:32.476 A:middle
goal.

00:29:32.476 --> 00:29:33.996 A:middle
But we approach them

00:29:34.316 --> 00:29:34.836 A:middle
differently.

00:29:35.056 --> 00:29:36.466 A:middle
Today, well, Today is going to

00:29:36.466 --> 00:29:37.416 A:middle
be updated every day.

00:29:37.636 --> 00:29:38.556 A:middle
Don't really have a choice

00:29:38.556 --> 00:29:38.866 A:middle
there.

00:29:38.866 --> 00:29:39.486 A:middle
Hence the name.

00:29:39.486 --> 00:29:42.066 A:middle
It's going to have a very

00:29:42.416 --> 00:29:43.536 A:middle
focused perspective.

00:29:43.536 --> 00:29:45.186 A:middle
It's going to be highly

00:29:45.186 --> 00:29:46.126 A:middle
contextual.

00:29:46.596 --> 00:29:48.326 A:middle
And when customers tap on cards

00:29:48.326 --> 00:29:50.096 A:middle
in Today, they can actually go

00:29:50.096 --> 00:29:52.436 A:middle
directly to buy that app or game

00:29:52.436 --> 00:29:53.126 A:middle
from the card.

00:29:53.376 --> 00:29:55.066 A:middle
Or of course, tap in and read

00:29:55.066 --> 00:29:56.156 A:middle
one of our stories.

00:29:56.936 --> 00:29:58.106 A:middle
The Games and Apps tabs are

00:29:58.106 --> 00:29:58.876 A:middle
going to be different.

00:29:59.126 --> 00:30:00.436 A:middle
In many ways you can think about

00:30:00.436 --> 00:30:03.076 A:middle
those as a 2.0 version or a

00:30:03.076 --> 00:30:04.406 A:middle
newly evolved version of the

00:30:04.406 --> 00:30:06.486 A:middle
Feature tab now, including

00:30:06.486 --> 00:30:08.116 A:middle
categories and including charts,

00:30:08.166 --> 00:30:08.956 A:middle
as you're seeing.

00:30:09.096 --> 00:30:10.186 A:middle
Well, the Games and Apps tabs

00:30:10.186 --> 00:30:11.346 A:middle
are going to be updated often.

00:30:11.636 --> 00:30:12.506 A:middle
Not every day.

00:30:12.956 --> 00:30:14.386 A:middle
But more often than the weekly

00:30:14.386 --> 00:30:16.366 A:middle
that you see in today's cadence.

00:30:16.646 --> 00:30:17.416 A:middle
Games and Apps are going to

00:30:17.416 --> 00:30:18.886 A:middle
offer a broader selection.

00:30:19.076 --> 00:30:20.386 A:middle
And it's generally going to be a

00:30:20.386 --> 00:30:22.006 A:middle
more transactional experience.

00:30:22.006 --> 00:30:23.966 A:middle
Taps on Games and Apps will take

00:30:23.966 --> 00:30:25.746 A:middle
customers directly to our

00:30:25.746 --> 00:30:27.496 A:middle
amazing new product pages.

00:30:29.576 --> 00:30:31.736 A:middle
Well, let me chat a little bit

00:30:31.736 --> 00:30:33.276 A:middle
about what we call our Story

00:30:33.596 --> 00:30:34.256 A:middle
Framework.

00:30:34.256 --> 00:30:35.996 A:middle
As you're seeing, stories on the

00:30:35.996 --> 00:30:37.436 A:middle
App Store will cover many, many

00:30:37.436 --> 00:30:37.926 A:middle
things.

00:30:38.086 --> 00:30:39.216 A:middle
We'll have world premieres.

00:30:39.216 --> 00:30:40.416 A:middle
We'll have major updates.

00:30:40.416 --> 00:30:41.746 A:middle
We'll have tips and tricks and

00:30:41.746 --> 00:30:43.026 A:middle
interviews with developers and

00:30:43.026 --> 00:30:44.086 A:middle
lists upon lists.

00:30:44.446 --> 00:30:46.076 A:middle
Well, our job is to write about

00:30:46.076 --> 00:30:47.056 A:middle
what we think customers will

00:30:47.056 --> 00:30:48.916 A:middle
find most interesting about an

00:30:48.916 --> 00:30:49.466 A:middle
app or a game.

00:30:49.466 --> 00:30:50.866 A:middle
And we really believe every app

00:30:50.866 --> 00:30:52.136 A:middle
has a story to tell.

00:30:53.386 --> 00:30:54.626 A:middle
There are four main topics of

00:30:54.626 --> 00:30:55.766 A:middle
stories for us.

00:30:56.176 --> 00:30:57.256 A:middle
When we think about all the

00:30:57.256 --> 00:30:58.806 A:middle
range, the broad, broad range of

00:30:58.806 --> 00:31:00.366 A:middle
ideas that we have, we try to

00:31:00.366 --> 00:31:02.426 A:middle
make -- we needed to make sense

00:31:02.426 --> 00:31:02.736 A:middle
of that.

00:31:02.736 --> 00:31:04.086 A:middle
So we started with just an idea

00:31:04.086 --> 00:31:04.726 A:middle
of topics.

00:31:04.946 --> 00:31:06.576 A:middle
What are the four main topics

00:31:06.576 --> 00:31:07.316 A:middle
that we will cover?

00:31:07.746 --> 00:31:09.386 A:middle
And for each topic we kind of

00:31:09.386 --> 00:31:10.526 A:middle
have a statement of belief.

00:31:11.026 --> 00:31:12.246 A:middle
This is something that we really

00:31:12.786 --> 00:31:15.246 A:middle
want to have customers feel in

00:31:15.246 --> 00:31:16.456 A:middle
the writing and the content that

00:31:16.456 --> 00:31:17.046 A:middle
we create.

00:31:17.046 --> 00:31:18.456 A:middle
Our first topic is, of course,

00:31:18.906 --> 00:31:19.506 A:middle
gaming.

00:31:19.746 --> 00:31:21.316 A:middle
Whether it's a big name game or

00:31:21.316 --> 00:31:22.376 A:middle
a small indie who has a

00:31:22.376 --> 00:31:23.856 A:middle
car-based strategy, RPG,

00:31:23.856 --> 00:31:25.616 A:middle
Infinite Runner, it doesn't

00:31:25.616 --> 00:31:25.866 A:middle
matter.

00:31:25.866 --> 00:31:26.976 A:middle
The games you make are so

00:31:26.976 --> 00:31:29.636 A:middle
innovative and so creative, our

00:31:29.636 --> 00:31:30.916 A:middle
game editors really believe

00:31:30.916 --> 00:31:31.346 A:middle
that, you know what?

00:31:31.346 --> 00:31:32.526 A:middle
Apps are the future of gaming.

00:31:32.726 --> 00:31:34.146 A:middle
In many ways apps are the

00:31:34.496 --> 00:31:35.566 A:middle
present of gaming.

00:31:35.726 --> 00:31:37.086 A:middle
Anyone agree with that comment?

00:31:37.086 --> 00:31:38.416 A:middle
Apps are the present of gaming?

00:31:39.876 --> 00:31:40.816 A:middle
Hey, we do have the biggest

00:31:40.816 --> 00:31:42.126 A:middle
gaming platform in the world.

00:31:42.126 --> 00:31:43.106 A:middle
And you know, we're very

00:31:43.106 --> 00:31:45.226 A:middle
enthusiastic about expressing to

00:31:45.226 --> 00:31:46.596 A:middle
our customers what we believe

00:31:46.736 --> 00:31:48.426 A:middle
the future is in games.

00:31:48.426 --> 00:31:51.016 A:middle
Our second topic: Lifestyle.

00:31:51.016 --> 00:31:52.036 A:middle
Well, what do we believe there?

00:31:52.036 --> 00:31:53.326 A:middle
Apps transform your life.

00:31:53.556 --> 00:31:54.726 A:middle
Whether it's social networking

00:31:54.726 --> 00:31:55.516 A:middle
or photography.

00:31:55.516 --> 00:31:56.686 A:middle
Whether it's dating or fitness

00:31:56.686 --> 00:31:58.556 A:middle
or cooking or transportation,

00:31:58.916 --> 00:32:01.136 A:middle
apps have helped us live in ways

00:32:01.136 --> 00:32:02.206 A:middle
that we've never, ever, ever

00:32:02.206 --> 00:32:03.046 A:middle
thought possible.

00:32:03.136 --> 00:32:04.636 A:middle
And we believe in our lifestyle

00:32:04.636 --> 00:32:06.336 A:middle
coverage that apps transform

00:32:06.586 --> 00:32:06.976 A:middle
your life.

00:32:08.066 --> 00:32:08.936 A:middle
Third, culture and

00:32:08.936 --> 00:32:09.426 A:middle
entertainment.

00:32:09.426 --> 00:32:10.796 A:middle
Apps shape culture.

00:32:10.796 --> 00:32:12.026 A:middle
Well, this is music, film,

00:32:12.026 --> 00:32:12.576 A:middle
fashion.

00:32:12.576 --> 00:32:14.366 A:middle
This is TV, pop culture and

00:32:14.366 --> 00:32:15.936 A:middle
everything in between.

00:32:16.256 --> 00:32:17.426 A:middle
The App Store is going to bring

00:32:17.426 --> 00:32:18.456 A:middle
all that together.

00:32:18.986 --> 00:32:20.276 A:middle
And so App Store [inaudible]

00:32:20.276 --> 00:32:22.296 A:middle
content may talk to celebrities.

00:32:22.576 --> 00:32:24.076 A:middle
We may talk to influencers.

00:32:24.196 --> 00:32:25.736 A:middle
We may talk to culture creators

00:32:25.736 --> 00:32:28.286 A:middle
of all kinds about the world of

00:32:28.286 --> 00:32:29.806 A:middle
apps and games because we

00:32:29.806 --> 00:32:31.626 A:middle
believe apps really do shape

00:32:31.626 --> 00:32:32.036 A:middle
culture.

00:32:32.786 --> 00:32:34.356 A:middle
And our fourth and final topic

00:32:34.356 --> 00:32:36.166 A:middle
is, of course, new tech and

00:32:36.166 --> 00:32:36.766 A:middle
innovation.

00:32:36.766 --> 00:32:38.096 A:middle
This is all things new, new,

00:32:38.096 --> 00:32:38.526 A:middle
new.

00:32:38.746 --> 00:32:39.546 A:middle
New services.

00:32:39.546 --> 00:32:40.326 A:middle
New ideas.

00:32:40.326 --> 00:32:41.356 A:middle
New capabilities.

00:32:41.666 --> 00:32:42.926 A:middle
Completely new ways of getting

00:32:42.926 --> 00:32:44.336 A:middle
things done with your iPhone or

00:32:44.336 --> 00:32:44.736 A:middle
iPad.

00:32:45.106 --> 00:32:46.516 A:middle
And we really feel that we can

00:32:46.516 --> 00:32:48.016 A:middle
provide a service to customers

00:32:48.246 --> 00:32:49.986 A:middle
to help them figure it all out.

00:32:50.296 --> 00:32:51.556 A:middle
Help them get great use out of

00:32:51.556 --> 00:32:52.856 A:middle
all the innovative work that you

00:32:52.856 --> 00:32:53.236 A:middle
do.

00:32:53.506 --> 00:32:54.836 A:middle
And help them potentially be

00:32:54.836 --> 00:32:57.056 A:middle
introduced into a whole new way

00:32:57.416 --> 00:32:58.276 A:middle
of doing things.

00:32:58.606 --> 00:33:00.026 A:middle
In many ways it's very Apple of

00:33:00.026 --> 00:33:00.286 A:middle
us.

00:33:00.286 --> 00:33:01.476 A:middle
We want to make the complex

00:33:01.476 --> 00:33:03.466 A:middle
world of technology simple.

00:33:04.416 --> 00:33:05.066 A:middle
All right.

00:33:05.066 --> 00:33:06.576 A:middle
Four topics: Gaming, lifestyle,

00:33:06.576 --> 00:33:07.736 A:middle
culture and entertainment, and

00:33:07.736 --> 00:33:08.896 A:middle
new tech and innovation.

00:33:09.256 --> 00:33:10.546 A:middle
When we take these topics, and

00:33:10.546 --> 00:33:12.456 A:middle
once we've decided on one, then

00:33:12.456 --> 00:33:14.056 A:middle
we want to apply what we call an

00:33:14.056 --> 00:33:14.836 A:middle
"intention."

00:33:14.836 --> 00:33:15.726 A:middle
And this is essentially the

00:33:15.726 --> 00:33:17.286 A:middle
purpose or the goal of each

00:33:17.286 --> 00:33:18.966 A:middle
story that you will see on the

00:33:18.966 --> 00:33:19.436 A:middle
App Store.

00:33:19.436 --> 00:33:20.376 A:middle
There are three of those.

00:33:20.746 --> 00:33:22.236 A:middle
The first we call "Inform."

00:33:22.636 --> 00:33:24.056 A:middle
This is about being timely.

00:33:24.356 --> 00:33:25.616 A:middle
This is about giving customers

00:33:25.616 --> 00:33:27.006 A:middle
"need-to-know" information.

00:33:27.246 --> 00:33:28.676 A:middle
This is to obviously let them

00:33:28.676 --> 00:33:29.736 A:middle
know what's happening in the

00:33:29.736 --> 00:33:31.086 A:middle
world right now.

00:33:31.316 --> 00:33:33.116 A:middle
For example, you can say a new

00:33:33.116 --> 00:33:34.826 A:middle
show is launching on Netflix.

00:33:34.826 --> 00:33:36.106 A:middle
And if we do that well, our

00:33:36.926 --> 00:33:38.186 A:middle
customer reaction may very

00:33:38.186 --> 00:33:39.456 A:middle
likely be: "Cool.

00:33:39.636 --> 00:33:41.746 A:middle
I want to get that."

00:33:41.746 --> 00:33:43.306 A:middle
Our second intention is simply

00:33:43.306 --> 00:33:44.046 A:middle
called "Help."

00:33:44.436 --> 00:33:45.666 A:middle
Really, really important for us.

00:33:45.666 --> 00:33:46.396 A:middle
This is about being

00:33:46.396 --> 00:33:47.096 A:middle
instructional.

00:33:47.096 --> 00:33:47.806 A:middle
This is about being

00:33:47.806 --> 00:33:48.526 A:middle
motivational.

00:33:48.926 --> 00:33:50.466 A:middle
This is about sharing ideas that

00:33:50.466 --> 00:33:52.556 A:middle
may be intuitive for us but not

00:33:52.556 --> 00:33:54.306 A:middle
for all of our customers.

00:33:54.556 --> 00:33:55.516 A:middle
How to get the most out of

00:33:55.516 --> 00:33:57.066 A:middle
Instagram's new feature could be

00:33:57.316 --> 00:33:58.176 A:middle
a helpful topic.

00:33:58.816 --> 00:34:00.886 A:middle
And for us, this can be a really

00:34:00.886 --> 00:34:03.126 A:middle
helpful way of reengaging our

00:34:03.126 --> 00:34:04.346 A:middle
customers with some apps that

00:34:04.346 --> 00:34:05.986 A:middle
they may have downloaded, may

00:34:05.986 --> 00:34:07.476 A:middle
knew they loved them, but

00:34:07.746 --> 00:34:08.866 A:middle
they've been left idle.

00:34:09.076 --> 00:34:10.356 A:middle
So how can we reengage our

00:34:10.356 --> 00:34:11.546 A:middle
customers with some of those

00:34:11.546 --> 00:34:13.556 A:middle
apps and even games by helping

00:34:13.556 --> 00:34:15.146 A:middle
them, giving them new ideas of

00:34:15.146 --> 00:34:17.116 A:middle
how to use one of these great

00:34:17.116 --> 00:34:17.546 A:middle
things?

00:34:18.636 --> 00:34:20.286 A:middle
And third, it's "Inspire."

00:34:20.706 --> 00:34:22.006 A:middle
This is going to be the topic

00:34:22.006 --> 00:34:23.886 A:middle
area or the intention where we

00:34:23.886 --> 00:34:25.486 A:middle
have really creative content,

00:34:25.816 --> 00:34:27.226 A:middle
really motivational content,

00:34:27.226 --> 00:34:27.986 A:middle
really insightful.

00:34:27.986 --> 00:34:28.816 A:middle
This is going to be everything

00:34:28.816 --> 00:34:29.976 A:middle
from a twelve-year-old making an

00:34:29.976 --> 00:34:31.606 A:middle
app to the 82-year-old making an

00:34:31.606 --> 00:34:33.806 A:middle
app, both of whom were here this

00:34:33.806 --> 00:34:34.226 A:middle
year.

00:34:34.446 --> 00:34:36.526 A:middle
This is inspiring content that

00:34:36.526 --> 00:34:39.006 A:middle
may go global around the world.

00:34:39.396 --> 00:34:41.676 A:middle
Inform, help and inspire.

00:34:41.866 --> 00:34:43.466 A:middle
If we inform, "Cool.

00:34:43.466 --> 00:34:44.416 A:middle
I want to get that."

00:34:44.416 --> 00:34:46.236 A:middle
If we help, "I had no idea.

00:34:46.236 --> 00:34:47.996 A:middle
Thanks." And if we inspire,

00:34:47.996 --> 00:34:48.546 A:middle
"Wow!

00:34:48.856 --> 00:34:49.876 A:middle
That's super interesting."

00:34:49.876 --> 00:34:51.046 A:middle
And of course, we are not going

00:34:51.046 --> 00:34:52.406 A:middle
to count any of those reactions

