But I'm happy to announce that

00:42:04.966 --> 00:42:07.536 A:middle
on AppStore.com/promote, that

00:42:07.536 --> 00:42:08.796 A:middle
will redirect to the new

00:42:08.796 --> 00:42:10.696 A:middle
Developer page where not only

00:42:10.696 --> 00:42:13.276 A:middle
will we ask you about your app

00:42:13.346 --> 00:42:14.806 A:middle
and your game and the features

00:42:14.806 --> 00:42:15.706 A:middle
and what's cool about it.

00:42:15.706 --> 00:42:17.756 A:middle
We'll also have a new area where

00:42:17.756 --> 00:42:19.276 A:middle
it says, "Tell us your story."

00:42:19.276 --> 00:42:20.886 A:middle
We're really, really excited to

