to share with us about your

00:42:24.256 --> 00:42:25.866 A:middle
creative process and what you

00:42:25.866 --> 00:42:26.556 A:middle
want to share with your

00:42:26.556 --> 00:42:28.496 A:middle
customers about apps and games.

00:42:28.756 --> 00:42:30.056 A:middle
So thank you so much.

00:42:30.056 --> 00:42:31.536 A:middle
We're really excited to be on

00:42:31.536 --> 00:42:32.556 A:middle
this journey together.

00:42:33.106 --> 00:42:33.886 A:middle
Thank you so much.

