I'd like now to bring back Mr.

00:42:37.076 --> 00:42:38.756 A:middle
Pedraum Pardehpoosh to bring us

00:42:38.756 --> 00:42:38.986 A:middle
home.

00:42:42.816 --> 00:42:43.346 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Thanks, Smokey.

00:42:44.766 --> 00:42:47.336 A:middle
So you heard some insights into

00:42:47.336 --> 00:42:49.126 A:middle
the why we did this redesign

00:42:49.326 --> 00:42:51.186 A:middle
from the lead designer herself.

00:42:51.186 --> 00:42:52.226 A:middle
This is a pretty special thing.

00:42:52.226 --> 00:42:53.386 A:middle
And you heard the insights from

00:42:53.386 --> 00:42:55.426 A:middle
Smokey about our doubling down

00:42:55.426 --> 00:42:56.246 A:middle
on editorial.

00:42:56.846 --> 00:42:59.536 A:middle
And got contact information for

00:42:59.536 --> 00:43:00.666 A:middle
how to get in touch with the

00:43:00.666 --> 00:43:01.396 A:middle
Editorial Team.

00:43:01.396 --> 00:43:02.726 A:middle
This is the dawn of a new day, I

00:43:02.726 --> 00:43:03.656 A:middle
think it's safe to say.

00:43:04.146 --> 00:43:05.216 A:middle
But let's not lose sight of the

00:43:05.266 --> 00:43:07.116 A:middle
fact that ultimately all of

00:43:07.116 --> 00:43:08.496 A:middle
these efforts are meant to

00:43:08.496 --> 00:43:09.826 A:middle
improve the discoverability of

00:43:09.826 --> 00:43:11.456 A:middle
apps and games on the App Store.

00:43:12.786 --> 00:43:13.956 A:middle
By giving people a reason to

00:43:13.956 --> 00:43:15.056 A:middle
come back to the App Store every

00:43:15.056 --> 00:43:17.236 A:middle
day and giving the context of

00:43:17.236 --> 00:43:17.826 A:middle
why we're making the

00:43:17.826 --> 00:43:18.916 A:middle
recommendations that we are.

00:43:19.466 --> 00:43:20.906 A:middle
This redesign is more than just

00:43:20.906 --> 00:43:21.856 A:middle
a facelift.

00:43:22.706 --> 00:43:24.056 A:middle
It's created new opportunities

00:43:24.056 --> 00:43:25.316 A:middle
to get discovered that haven't

00:43:25.316 --> 00:43:26.166 A:middle
existed before.

00:43:26.166 --> 00:43:27.276 A:middle
Whether it's being included in

00:43:27.276 --> 00:43:28.506 A:middle
one of the stories that Smokey

00:43:28.506 --> 00:43:30.596 A:middle
outlined or appearing in the new

00:43:30.596 --> 00:43:32.276 A:middle
Apps and Games tabs, which give

00:43:32.276 --> 00:43:33.716 A:middle
focus to each of those areas.

00:43:34.806 --> 00:43:35.706 A:middle
But as always, you shouldn't

00:43:35.706 --> 00:43:37.036 A:middle
just rely on being featured by

00:43:37.036 --> 00:43:39.776 A:middle
the App Store to improve your

00:43:39.776 --> 00:43:40.266 A:middle
app discovery.

00:43:40.266 --> 00:43:41.796 A:middle
There's things you can do even

00:43:41.796 --> 00:43:43.826 A:middle
starting now to get ready for

00:43:43.826 --> 00:43:44.306 A:middle
the new App Store.

00:43:44.306 --> 00:43:44.996 A:middle
And we're going to talk just a

00:43:44.996 --> 00:43:45.976 A:middle
couple minutes about them.

00:43:46.856 --> 00:43:47.756 A:middle
The first thing is in-app

00:43:47.756 --> 00:43:48.396 A:middle
purchases.

