By way of quick review, in-app

00:43:50.366 --> 00:43:51.666 A:middle
purchases now have a presence on

00:43:51.666 --> 00:43:52.246 A:middle
the App Store.

00:43:52.246 --> 00:43:53.576 A:middle
They can appear on the product

00:43:53.576 --> 00:43:54.436 A:middle
details page.

00:43:55.626 --> 00:43:57.036 A:middle
In featured content areas.

00:43:57.036 --> 00:43:58.166 A:middle
In search results.

00:43:59.366 --> 00:44:00.606 A:middle
And on your product page, excuse

00:44:01.416 --> 00:44:01.506 A:middle
me.

00:44:02.936 --> 00:44:05.176 A:middle
This new ability combined with

00:44:05.176 --> 00:44:06.846 A:middle
the new Subscriptions features

00:44:07.256 --> 00:44:08.256 A:middle
that we announced last year,

00:44:08.256 --> 00:44:09.606 A:middle
giving you brand new

00:44:09.606 --> 00:44:10.626 A:middle
opportunities for creating

00:44:10.626 --> 00:44:11.576 A:middle
sustainable businesses.

00:44:12.866 --> 00:44:14.076 A:middle
So you'll want to start thinking

00:44:14.286 --> 00:44:16.056 A:middle
now about the title of these

00:44:16.056 --> 00:44:17.006 A:middle
in-app purchases and the

00:44:17.006 --> 00:44:18.746 A:middle
description and the image that

00:44:18.746 --> 00:44:21.996 A:middle
you're going to use for them,

00:44:22.266 --> 00:44:23.346 A:middle
particularly now that they have

00:44:23.346 --> 00:44:24.506 A:middle
such increased visibility.

00:44:25.626 --> 00:44:26.886 A:middle
There's a couple of StoreKit

00:44:26.886 --> 00:44:29.036 A:middle
sessions and an iTunes Connect

00:44:29.036 --> 00:44:29.866 A:middle
session where you can get more

00:44:29.866 --> 00:44:30.806 A:middle
information about this.

00:44:31.976 --> 00:44:33.056 A:middle
We'll review those at the end.

00:44:33.906 --> 00:44:35.436 A:middle
Titles are now 30 characters in

00:44:35.436 --> 00:44:36.516 A:middle
the App Store, in the all new

00:44:36.516 --> 00:44:37.006 A:middle
App Store.

00:44:37.856 --> 00:44:38.876 A:middle
But in addition, you will have a

00:44:38.876 --> 00:44:39.506 A:middle
subtitle.

00:44:40.676 --> 00:44:42.286 A:middle
Monika showed this in context as

00:44:42.286 --> 00:44:42.786 A:middle
well.

00:44:43.176 --> 00:44:44.276 A:middle
You'll want to think carefully

00:44:44.276 --> 00:44:45.956 A:middle
about how to use this subtitle

00:44:46.576 --> 00:44:47.886 A:middle
to convey what your app does.

00:44:47.886 --> 00:44:48.856 A:middle
To give a little bit more

00:44:48.856 --> 00:44:49.716 A:middle
information about it.

00:44:49.716 --> 00:44:51.126 A:middle
To say something compelling.

00:44:51.126 --> 00:44:52.936 A:middle
But don't be misleading.

00:44:55.536 --> 00:44:57.236 A:middle
Consider using your subtitle to

00:44:57.236 --> 00:44:58.876 A:middle
highlight a feature or a typical

00:44:58.876 --> 00:45:00.966 A:middle
use of your app that'll resonate

00:45:00.966 --> 00:45:01.656 A:middle
with your audience.

00:45:02.686 --> 00:45:03.946 A:middle
And this subtitle will follow

00:45:03.946 --> 00:45:05.276 A:middle
your app title around throughout

00:45:05.276 --> 00:45:07.776 A:middle
the app store, whether it's in

00:45:07.776 --> 00:45:10.046 A:middle
the Apps or the Games tab, on a

00:45:10.046 --> 00:45:11.226 A:middle
product page or in search

00:45:11.226 --> 00:45:11.736 A:middle
results.

00:45:12.286 --> 00:45:15.596 A:middle
Let's talk about video app

00:45:15.596 --> 00:45:16.116 A:middle
previews.

00:45:16.396 --> 00:45:17.526 A:middle
We know that when customers

00:45:17.526 --> 00:45:18.686 A:middle
engage with these video app

00:45:18.726 --> 00:45:21.586 A:middle
previews, customers tend to

00:45:21.986 --> 00:45:24.176 A:middle
download that app or game more.

00:45:25.256 --> 00:45:26.316 A:middle
And so we thought about, "Well,

00:45:26.316 --> 00:45:27.876 A:middle
how can we make it more obvious

00:45:27.876 --> 00:45:28.646 A:middle
that these are videos?"

00:45:29.796 --> 00:45:30.886 A:middle
Well, auto-playing is one way

00:45:30.886 --> 00:45:31.416 A:middle
you can do that.

00:45:32.596 --> 00:45:34.296 A:middle
And so we really encourage you,

00:45:34.296 --> 00:45:35.206 A:middle
particularly now that you can

00:45:35.206 --> 00:45:35.946 A:middle
have three of them.

00:45:37.246 --> 00:45:38.476 A:middle
And they can be localized.

00:45:39.636 --> 00:45:40.516 A:middle
You should really be thinking

00:45:40.516 --> 00:45:42.926 A:middle
about how to create a video that

00:45:43.236 --> 00:45:44.636 A:middle
encourages customers to download

00:45:45.276 --> 00:45:48.956 A:middle
your app or game.

00:45:50.596 --> 00:45:51.906 A:middle
We think video is a big deal on

00:45:51.906 --> 00:45:52.456 A:middle
the App Store.

00:45:55.036 --> 00:45:55.826 A:middle
You can learn more about what

00:45:55.826 --> 00:45:56.946 A:middle
makes a compelling video by

00:45:56.946 --> 00:45:58.466 A:middle
visiting the site, and by

00:45:58.466 --> 00:45:59.626 A:middle
visiting the App Store labs.

