Now, in addition to your app

00:46:04.246 --> 00:46:06.696 A:middle
description, you can have 170

00:46:06.696 --> 00:46:08.166 A:middle
characters of text, which can be

00:46:08.166 --> 00:46:08.926 A:middle
updated any time.

00:46:08.926 --> 00:46:10.126 A:middle
We call this Promo Text.

00:46:10.746 --> 00:46:11.836 A:middle
This will get concatenated on

00:46:11.836 --> 00:46:13.186 A:middle
top of your app description.

00:46:14.286 --> 00:46:15.376 A:middle
And it won't require an app

00:46:15.376 --> 00:46:15.866 A:middle
update.

00:46:17.576 --> 00:46:18.706 A:middle
This is a great way to talk

00:46:18.706 --> 00:46:19.646 A:middle
about one of the new features

00:46:19.646 --> 00:46:20.896 A:middle
that's a temporary feature or a

00:46:20.896 --> 00:46:21.896 A:middle
price promotion that you're

00:46:21.896 --> 00:46:23.566 A:middle
having or some new accolade that

00:46:23.566 --> 00:46:24.516 A:middle
your app has received.

00:46:25.356 --> 00:46:26.216 A:middle
This is something else that you

00:46:26.216 --> 00:46:27.216 A:middle
can start thinking about right

00:46:27.216 --> 00:46:27.496 A:middle
now.

00:46:28.416 --> 00:46:31.596 A:middle
Let's talk about ratings and

00:46:31.596 --> 00:46:31.856 A:middle
reviews.

00:46:31.856 --> 00:46:32.746 A:middle
This got some applause.

00:46:32.826 --> 00:46:35.416 A:middle
This warms my heart.

00:46:35.656 --> 00:46:36.856 A:middle
We did a couple things in iOS

00:46:36.856 --> 00:46:40.316 A:middle
10.3 releasing a Reviews API.

00:46:42.116 --> 00:46:43.726 A:middle
And allowing developers to

00:46:43.726 --> 00:46:44.746 A:middle
respond to reviews.

00:46:44.746 --> 00:46:45.906 A:middle
And the response has been

00:46:45.906 --> 00:46:46.406 A:middle
tremendous.

00:46:47.256 --> 00:46:49.696 A:middle
We've seen almost 400,000 --

00:46:49.916 --> 00:46:51.166 A:middle
this number's actually a little

00:46:51.166 --> 00:46:51.566 A:middle
old.

00:46:52.086 --> 00:46:53.496 A:middle
We've seen almost 400,000

00:46:53.886 --> 00:46:56.046 A:middle
responses to reviews since the

00:46:56.046 --> 00:46:56.506 A:middle
launch of this.

00:46:56.506 --> 00:46:57.706 A:middle
And we know that when customers

00:46:57.706 --> 00:47:00.106 A:middle
go back and change their rating

00:47:00.106 --> 00:47:01.626 A:middle
based on a response that they

00:47:01.626 --> 00:47:02.846 A:middle
have received from a developer,

00:47:03.326 --> 00:47:06.146 A:middle
overwhelmingly that change in

00:47:06.146 --> 00:47:07.426 A:middle
direction is in a positive way.

00:47:08.416 --> 00:47:12.226 A:middle
So this is really important.

00:47:13.296 --> 00:47:14.736 A:middle
In the new App Store, as Monika

00:47:14.736 --> 00:47:16.026 A:middle
mentioned, we no longer reset

00:47:16.026 --> 00:47:17.216 A:middle
app rating when you submit a new

00:47:17.216 --> 00:47:17.726 A:middle
version.

00:47:18.826 --> 00:47:19.956 A:middle
Which is awesome for many

00:47:19.956 --> 00:47:20.456 A:middle
developers.

00:47:20.456 --> 00:47:22.676 A:middle
Some developers wouldn't mind

00:47:23.306 --> 00:47:24.166 A:middle
resetting that rating.

00:47:25.196 --> 00:47:26.716 A:middle
And now, with the new App Store,

00:47:27.276 --> 00:47:28.236 A:middle
with each submission you're

00:47:28.236 --> 00:47:29.326 A:middle
going to have the ability to do

00:47:29.326 --> 00:47:30.616 A:middle
so, to reset your rating.

00:47:31.456 --> 00:47:32.406 A:middle
But you should be careful about

00:47:32.406 --> 00:47:32.576 A:middle
that.

00:47:32.576 --> 00:47:34.276 A:middle
It sounds like an interesting

00:47:34.276 --> 00:47:34.716 A:middle
option.

00:47:34.716 --> 00:47:36.346 A:middle
But we know that customers value

00:47:36.806 --> 00:47:39.726 A:middle
that rating or seeing that an

00:47:39.726 --> 00:47:41.466 A:middle
app has ratings, a lot, when

00:47:41.466 --> 00:47:42.166 A:middle
they're making a download

00:47:42.166 --> 00:47:42.526 A:middle
decision.

00:47:42.526 --> 00:47:44.396 A:middle
So you will want to be careful

00:47:44.956 --> 00:47:47.666 A:middle
about that.

00:47:47.886 --> 00:47:49.456 A:middle
You can get advice about best

00:47:49.456 --> 00:47:50.906 A:middle
practices associated with

00:47:51.336 --> 00:47:52.706 A:middle
responding to customer reviews

00:47:52.706 --> 00:47:54.796 A:middle
by visiting this URL.

00:47:56.356 --> 00:47:58.576 A:middle
And like we mentioned, we

00:47:58.576 --> 00:47:59.936 A:middle
strongly recommend you make

00:47:59.936 --> 00:48:01.826 A:middle
responding to customer reviews a

00:48:01.826 --> 00:48:02.846 A:middle
regular part of your customer

00:48:02.846 --> 00:48:03.666 A:middle
service hygiene.

00:48:04.426 --> 00:48:06.396 A:middle
And in fact, in July, in iTunes

00:48:06.396 --> 00:48:08.356 A:middle
Connect, we'll be enabling a new

00:48:08.356 --> 00:48:10.906 A:middle
role in iTunes Connect for

00:48:10.906 --> 00:48:12.816 A:middle
customer service so that you can

00:48:12.816 --> 00:48:14.016 A:middle
have somebody that's focused

00:48:14.016 --> 00:48:14.936 A:middle
just on that and doesn't have

00:48:14.936 --> 00:48:17.786 A:middle
access to other elements inside

00:48:18.606 --> 00:48:18.696 A:middle
there.

00:48:19.576 --> 00:48:21.666 A:middle
We're constantly improving the

00:48:21.666 --> 00:48:22.776 A:middle
way Core Search works in the

00:48:22.776 --> 00:48:23.286 A:middle
Apps Store.

00:48:23.606 --> 00:48:24.766 A:middle
But the most visible thing we've

00:48:24.766 --> 00:48:27.256 A:middle
done this year is by adding the

00:48:27.256 --> 00:48:28.446 A:middle
stories that our editors are

00:48:28.446 --> 00:48:28.776 A:middle
writing.

00:48:30.416 --> 00:48:31.956 A:middle
Additionally, in-app purchases,

00:48:31.956 --> 00:48:34.006 A:middle
categories and developers will

00:48:34.006 --> 00:48:35.186 A:middle
be able to appear in these

00:48:35.186 --> 00:48:38.236 A:middle
search results as well.

00:48:38.436 --> 00:48:40.986 A:middle
Speaking of search, last year we

00:48:40.986 --> 00:48:42.226 A:middle
announced Search Ads.

00:48:43.046 --> 00:48:44.266 A:middle
And it launched in the US.

00:48:45.736 --> 00:48:46.716 A:middle
And it launched in the UK,

00:48:46.716 --> 00:48:47.736 A:middle
Australia and New Zealand in

00:48:47.736 --> 00:48:48.046 A:middle
April.

00:48:49.426 --> 00:48:50.606 A:middle
The results have been really

00:48:50.606 --> 00:48:51.796 A:middle
strong for advertisers.

