And cost per acquisition just

00:48:57.806 --> 00:48:58.406 A:middle
over a dollar.

00:48:58.406 --> 00:48:59.866 A:middle
These are really impressive

00:48:59.866 --> 00:49:01.266 A:middle
numbers for those that know

00:49:01.266 --> 00:49:02.366 A:middle
stuff about advertising.

