An apps flyer industry study

00:49:04.436 --> 00:49:05.816 A:middle
published earlier this year

00:49:06.066 --> 00:49:07.556 A:middle
described the quality of users

00:49:07.556 --> 00:49:08.886 A:middle
Search Ads delivers were the

00:49:08.886 --> 00:49:10.676 A:middle
best 30-day retention rate for

00:49:10.676 --> 00:49:12.926 A:middle
iOS apps and a top three ranking

00:49:12.926 --> 00:49:13.526 A:middle
for games.

00:49:15.436 --> 00:49:16.596 A:middle
We're working hard to deliver

00:49:16.596 --> 00:49:17.836 A:middle
opportunities to drive downloads

00:49:17.836 --> 00:49:18.816 A:middle
and engagement with your apps.

00:49:18.886 --> 00:49:20.316 A:middle
And bringing Search Ads to more

00:49:20.316 --> 00:49:22.146 A:middle
of the markets that you've told

00:49:22.146 --> 00:49:22.966 A:middle
us are important to your

00:49:22.966 --> 00:49:23.296 A:middle
business.

00:49:23.956 --> 00:49:25.416 A:middle
Many developers large and small

00:49:25.416 --> 00:49:26.476 A:middle
have already taken advantage of

00:49:26.476 --> 00:49:26.596 A:middle
it.

00:49:26.596 --> 00:49:27.596 A:middle
And this is another thing you'll

00:49:27.596 --> 00:49:28.976 A:middle
want to consult with us about to

00:49:29.026 --> 00:49:32.876 A:middle
find out if it's right for you.

00:49:32.876 --> 00:49:34.556 A:middle
In summary, there's plenty for

00:49:34.556 --> 00:49:35.766 A:middle
you to be thinking about even

00:49:35.766 --> 00:49:37.436 A:middle
now in advance of iOS 11

00:49:37.436 --> 00:49:39.966 A:middle
shipping as it relates to your

00:49:39.966 --> 00:49:40.976 A:middle
app's presence in the Apps.

00:49:40.976 --> 00:49:42.016 A:middle
And we hope you take advantage

00:49:42.016 --> 00:49:43.016 A:middle
of the folks that are here from

